# Self-Corrected Rule Rollback Controller

## Purpose
Provide a controlled mechanism to deactivate or revert unsafe, harmful,
or low-value self-corrected rules.

---

# WHEN TO TRIGGER ROLLBACK REVIEW

Trigger review if:

1. A self-corrected rule causes:
   - Repeated false positives
   - Over-restriction
   - Blocked valid solutions
   - Conflict loops
   - Reduced solution quality

OR

